646
00:31:46,509 --> 00:31:49,262
Mirren: Ours is
a richly diverse world,

647
00:31:49,262 --> 00:31:51,806
comprised
of countless creatures,

648
00:31:51,806 --> 00:31:54,100
each with their own
animating principle,

649
00:31:54,100 --> 00:31:57,937
a purpose, a calling,

650
00:31:57,937 --> 00:32:00,273
a reason for being.

651
