712
00:34:28,421 --> 00:34:30,756
Right now, I wouldn't
disagree with him.

713
00:34:30,756 --> 00:34:33,175
Fish. Fish.
Get it. Get it.

714
00:34:33,175 --> 00:34:35,594
Dad, Dad, he's gone.

715
00:34:35,594 --> 00:34:38,347
Why does this happen
