716
00:34:38,347 --> 00:34:42,601
♪♪

717
00:34:42,601 --> 00:34:44,729
Mirren: The pressures
of raising offspring,

718
00:34:44,729 --> 00:34:46,981
both human and animal,

719
00:34:46,981 --> 00:34:50,568
