for one of those things?

725
00:35:05,291 --> 00:35:07,501
I mean, I could totally do it.

726
00:35:07,501 --> 00:35:09,670
Bleep‐blorp, bleep‐blorp.

727
00:35:09,670 --> 00:35:10,880
See?

728
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:13,215
Super easy. Come on.

729
